---
import Button from "../components/ui/Button.astro";
import LinkButton from "../components/LinkButton.astro";
---

<section
  data-testid="hero"
  class="flex flex-col-reverse items-center justify-center text-center lg:flex-row"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center py-10 lg:mb-0">
    <div>
      <p class="p-6 text-xl">
        My name is <span class="font-bold text-skin-accent">Sam-Oladapo Ebenezer</span>. 
        I am a Software Engineer with a background in Electrical and Electronic Engineering. 
        I work across <span class="font-bold text-skin-accent">cloud architecture, distributed systems, compilers, video engineering,</span> 
        and <span class="font-bold text-skin-accent">performance optimization</span>. 
        I contribute to open-source and have shipped production software used by large user bases.
      </p>
      <p class="p-6 text-xl">
        I am passionate about building reliable, scalable systems and enabling 
        teams to be highly productive. My interests include 
        <LinkButton
          className="hover:text-skin-accent"
          href="/tags/kubernetes"
        >
          Kubernetes,
        </LinkButton>
        <span class="font-bold text-skin-accent"><a href="/tags/systems-programming">Systems Programming</a></span>, 
        <span class="font-bold text-skin-accent"><a href="/tags/software-engineering">Software Engineering</a></span>, 
        and exploring new approaches to software design and optimization.
      </p>
      <p class="p-6 text-xl">
        Outside of engineering, I enjoy <span class="font-bold text-skin-accent">travelling</span> 
        to explore new cultures and <span class="font-bold text-skin-accent">cooking</span> 
        as a creative outlet.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-0">
      <Button
        onclick="window.location.href='/about';"
        style={"primary"}
        size={"lg"}
        class={"flex"}
        name="learn more"
        href="/about"
      >
        Learn more
      </Button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
